       Night Ride  Transportation option offered after the operational hours of our bus circuit.             UI Ride  UI Ride is an intercampus shuttle that provides transportation between Chicago and Urbana-Champaign.             Campus Auto Rental Service  The Campus Auto Rental Service provides vehicles for use on university business.             Chauffeur Service  Chauffeur Services are available to UIC faculty, staff and students.             Abandoned Bicycle Removal  Policy on the removal of abandoned bicycles.             Moving Service  All moving services can be requested by submitting a billable service request through FMWeb.             Map   Address: Transportation Facility (MC 269), 1351 South Morgan Street, Chicago, IL 60607 Phone: (312) 99 6-2842 — Fax: (312) 996-0165 Office Hours: 7:00AM to 5:00PM (CT) Monday through Friday                       UIC Logo        Transportation         Policies    Web Privacy Notice      Related Links    Facilities Management    Office of the Vice Chancellor of Administrative Services         Contact   1351 South Morgan Street  Phone: (312) 996-2842  Fax: (312) 996-0165  rides@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts             UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  © 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings                 